    .sinuswave-hr-tiny.mt-3.mb-3

    .row
      .col
        We have absolutely
        %strong no commercial intent
        on this project.

    .sinuswave-hr-tiny.mt-3.mb-3

    .row
      .col
        We made this application to
        %strong learn
        and for
        = succeed '.' do
