    .row
      .col
        We are very sorry for any bugs.
        %strong Let us know
        if you find one (see email address below).

    .sinuswave-hr-tiny.mt-3.mb-3

    .row
      .col
        If you have comments, questions or love to share
        please write us an email to
    .row.mt-3
      .col
